// Stove Endpoints

### Get All Stoves
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves

### Get Stove by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1

### Get Stove by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/99999

### Get Stove by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/invalid

### Get Player's Stoves
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/stoves

### Get Player's Stoves (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/stoves

### Get Stoves by Type
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/stoves

### Get Stoves by Type (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/invalid/stoves

### Create Stove (Mint)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stoves
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "typeId": 1,
    "currentOwnerId": 1
}

### Create Stove (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stoves
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "typeId": 1
}

### Transfer Ownership
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1/owner
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "newOwnerId": 2
}

### Transfer Ownership (missing fields)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1/owner
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Transfer Ownership (not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/99999/owner
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "newOwnerId": 2
}

### Delete Stove
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1

### Delete Stove (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/99999

### Count Player's Stoves
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/stoves/count

### Count Player's Stoves (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/stoves/count

### Count Stoves by Type
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/stoves/count

### Count Stoves by Type (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/invalid/stoves/count
